    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing it with the side of a knife</p><p>Combine your<strong> egg[s]</strong> with 35g<span class=\"text-purple\"> [50g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[70g]</span><strong> flour</strong> and 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>milk </strong>in a jug, then whisk in your <strong>dried thyme</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> – this is your<strong> batter</strong></p><p>Put the <strong>batter</strong> in the fridge to rest</p>",
