      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>roasted duck leg </strong>with the <strong>duck fat roasties</strong>, <strong>herby</strong> <strong>Yorkshires</strong>, <strong>red cabbage </strong>and <strong>cooked green beans </strong>to the side</p><p>Discard the <strong>crushed garlic</strong> from the <strong>garlic-infused gravy </strong>and drizzle all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
